					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2527320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203757" alt="LordStonefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2527320)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;" >LordStonefish</a></span> <span class="odate time_1472784480 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 Sep 2016 02:48</span>
